title: Be'lakor - The Frail Tide [2007] - (Belakor Be'lakor)
description:
First Album Ive ever bothered to upload to a tracker site and seed. This album isnt available to buy anywhere at the moment, or download. 

Ill seed this for as long as possible. Cant imagine any metal fans who would dislike this album, so tell your friends about it too. Damn good up and coming band!
